description:
One of the most powerful fused characters, Vegito (SSGSS), enters the world of DRAGON BALL FighterZ!

This content includes:
• Vegito (SSGSS) as a new playable character
• 5 alternative colors for his outfit
• Vegito (SSGSS) Lobby Avatar
• Vegito (SSGSS) Z Stamp
name: DRAGON BALL FIGHTERZ - Vegito (SSGSS)
